## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all cultural contexts or perspectives. The information is also limited to the data available up to October 2023, and newer developments or studies may not be included. Additionally, the reliance on educational platforms and public forums may introduce biases based on the contributors' perspectives. Further research, including peer-reviewed studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

